Firamiya minsintan Indiya zai halarci kafa ginshikin wani sabon gurin bauta a wajen da ake takadama akai
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin aza harsashin ginin wurin bautar Hindu a watan mai zuwa a wani wurin da ake takaddama da ke arewacin Indiya a inda a da, wannan wurin wania masallaci ne aka rugurguza shi karni na 16 wanda wasu masu tsattsauran ra'ayi na Hindu su ka yi a 1992, kamar yadda aka ji daga masu amintattu daaka dorawa alhakkin kula da ginin.
An shirya gudanar da bikin a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya bikin su kace tana da matukar fa'ida aga Hindu bisa bincikensu na ilimin taurari sai dai hakan kuma ya daidai da cika shekara guda tun bayan da majalisar kasar Indiyan ta soke matsayin jiha na mai dauke da mafiya yawan musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Ba zai yiwu wannan alama ya zama arashi ba ga magoya baya da kuma 'yan adawan Jam'iyyar Modi ta Bharatiya Janata ko kuma BJP ba, wanda manufar jam'iyyarsu na tsawon shekara-da shekaru ya hada da alkawarin kwace ikon Kashmir na cin gashin kanta da kuma gina gurin bauta ga gunkin Hindu watau Ram a inda a da masallacin na zamanin mulkin Mugahl yake, wani wurin cikin birnin Ayodhya dake Jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda mabiya addinin su ka yi imanin da cewa nan ne mahaifar Ram.
Sakamakon annobar cutar korona wacce take ci gaba da yaduwa a duk fadin Indiyan, wanda kuma aka bayar da rahoton cewa ita ce ta uku a duniya mafi yawan wadanada suka kamu, za'a watsa bikin kai tsaye a gidan talabijin na jihar sannan kuma za'a takaitayawan masu halartar bikin da kuma kallo, cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar yan kishin Hindu da ke kawance da jam'iyyar BJP.
Wurin bautar zai kasance a matsayin wata "cibiya mai dorewa da kuma samar da dauwamammen hadin kai, na jin dadin al'umma, da hadin kan kasa, da habaka, da farkar, da kuma kaunar 'yan Hindutva," ko kuma hanyar rayuwar 'yan Hindu, kamar yadda kakakin kungiyar Vinod Bamsal ya bayyana cikin wata sanarwa da aak rabawa manema labarai da aka fitar  a ranar Asabar.
An kawo karshen takaddama kan wurin na sama da karni a shekarar da ta wuce bayan samun wani gagarumin nasarar da jam'iyyar BJP ta yi a zaben da aka yi.
Cikin watan Nuwamba ne kotun koli ta kasar ta yanke hukunci na goyon bayan gina wurin bautar, tana cewa za ta baiwa Musulmai wadanda suka shigar da wani filin mai girman eka biyar a wani wurin na daban.
Masu tsatstsauran ra'ayin na addinin Hindu sun dade suna jayayya kan cewa masu mamaya Musulman Mughal ne gina masallaci akan wani ginin wurin bauta a birnin Ayodya mai tsohon tarihi.
A shekarar 1992 ne a watan Disamba ruguza Masallacin ya haddasa rikicin kabilanci wanda kusan mutane 2,000 suka rasa rayukansu, mafi yawan su musulmai.
A halin yanzu dai, ana ci gaba da sauraron karar rusa gini a wata kotu daban ta musamman.
Wani Mai zanen gine-gine daga Ahmedabad, da ke Gujurat, jihar da aka haifi Modi, ya gabatar da wani tsarin gini babba na dutsin sandstoe mai tsayin kafa 162 (mita 49) da ke dauke dahubbare guda biya.
BWani babban minista kuma malamin addinin Hindu na Uttar Pradesh, Yogi Adityanath, ya nemi cewa 'yan garin Ayodhya su yi wani bikin tsarkake da kuma tsaftace na musamman, sannan kuma a duk wuraren bautar da ke garin, sai suma su kunna fitulun aci bal-bal gabanin ziyarar Modi, rahoton kamfanin dillancin labarai na Press Trust Indiya.
A cewar PTI - Adityanath na mai cewa bikin zai yi nuni da kawo karshen "gwagwarmaya ta shekaru 500".
