An cinnawa wata Kotu wuta a yayin zanga-zanga a California
OAKLAND, Ca. Wasu masu zanga-zanga sun cinnawa ginin wata kotu wuta, da lalata wani ofishin 'yan sanda da kuma kai hari kan su, a yayin da wata zanga-zangar lumana ta yi tsanani a yammacin Asabar, a cewar 'yan sanda Oakland.
Masu zanga-zangar sun farfasa wunduna, sun yi zane-zanen batanci, sun kuma harba abin wasan wuta mai tartsatsi ga jami'an 'yansanda. A cewar hukumar ta Oakland a dandalin Tuwita.
Sakonnin Tuwita da yawa da aka aika na kiran da a zauna lafiya da kuma kira ga wadanda suka shirya zanga-zangar da su "taimaka da mu samar sa wurare marasa hadari da kuma wurare marasa hadari ga maus zanga-zangar"
Da farko an soma zanga-zangar ne da la'asar sakaliya tare da kungiyoyi kamar su "Bangon iyaye mata", makamanaciyar wacce aka kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayain da masu zanga-zangar su kayi gaba-gaba da jami'an gwamnatin ta kasa da aka turo don su tsare ginin kotun ta gwamnatin tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya aika da jamai'an gwmanatin tarayyar ne domin su tarwatsa masu zanga-zangar ne da ake ta yi da darea tun kisan George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
An soma zanga-zangar ta Oakland cikn lumana, amma kuma ya rikide ya koma tarzoma.
'Yan sanda sun ayyana dokar"taruwa ba bisa ka'ida ba" da misalin 11:30 na dare, sannan jami'an 'yan sandan suka ce da jama'ar da ta taru da su watse.
Gobarar ta tashi ne a babban kotun gundumar Alameda an kuma kasheta a cikin kankanin lokaci, a cewar kafofin yada labarai.
'Yan sanda suka ce, a na tsaka da zanga-zangar sai mai suka shiga "farfasa wunduna da kuma wake-waken batanci ga mazauna wurin."
Hotunan da 'yan sandan ta yada a dandalin Tuwita ya nuna fasassun gilasai da fentin da aka watsawa wani gini na 'yan sanda.
An tsaurara matakan tsaro a kofara ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu, a China
An tsaurara matakan tsaro a kofar shiga ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu, a China a ranar Lahadi, yayin da Amurkawa ma'aikatan ofishin ke shirin barin ofishin.
An ga wasu mayan motocin daukar kaya suna shiga cikin ginin ofishin yayin da wasu jami'an tsaro sanye da kayan sarki da kuma wasu 'yan sanda cikin farin kaya sun jeru a hagu da dama titin, wanda aka yi masa shige na karfe.
