Daya daga cikin manyan bankunan Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta "shirya gadar zare" ga kamfanin Huawei na China cikin binciken da Amurka take yi - Labaran Kasuwanci na RT
Landan- Babban Shalkwatar bankin HSBC na kasa da kasa ya bayyana a kafofin sada zumunta cewa kamar yadda kafofin watsa labaran China su ka yi "Ikirarin shaida" a kan Huawei ba haka bane, inda abin ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudin kamfanin na Canada.
Cikin wani sako na WeChat wanda yanzu ba'a samu, mai bayar da rancen ya ce aiyukan da ta yi ba su suka haifar da binciken da Amurka take yiwa babban kamfanin samar da kayayyakin sadarwa na duniya ba, illa bincikar kamfanin kan zargin watsi da takunkumin da Amurka ta sanyawa Iran akan Huawei ya fara tun kafin bankin ya shigo cikin karshen a shekarar 2016.
A ranar Asabar bankin na mai cewa, "HSBC ba ta da wata kiyayya dangane da Huawei kuma ba ta shiryawa Huawei "gadar zare ba," ya kara da cewa ba zai taba boye gaskiyar ba daganne da abokan huldarsa ba.
"Duba da bukatar US DOJ [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka na neman bayani, gungun kamfanin HSBC cikin sauki ya gabatar da gaskiyar manufar kawai ce kawai.
HSBC ba ta "kirkiri" shaida ko kuma "boye" gaskiya ba."
A rt.com kuma yunkurin Birtaniya na haramtawa kamfanin Huawei fito da fasahar sadarwa ta 5G ya nuna tasirin Amurka a kan manufofin kasashen waje na Birtaniya - George Galloway ga Boom Bust
An toshe sakon a shafin a dandalin tare da bayanin cewa "ya sabawa ka'idoji" yanzu kuma babu shi.
Wannan bayanin ya fito ne bayan da kafofin yada labarai na China da suka hada da jaridun dake da alaka da gwamati suka zargi HSBC da "kitsa" makarkashiya tare da Washington don kulla wa Huawei gadar zare.
Kamfanin ya fada tsakiyar rikicin badkala ta diflomasiya na tsawon shekara daya da rabi tun da aka tsare Meng Wanzhou, wani babban Jami'in Hada-hadar kudi a watan Disamba ta shekarar 2018 a Canada daga wata takardar sammaci daga Amurka.
Meng yana fuskantar tuhuma a kan zargin yin amfani da kamfanin shell don karya takunkumin da aka sa wa Iran da kuma zargin yiwa bankuna karya dangane da alakar da ke tsakanin kamafanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran Skycom.
A cewar wata sabuwar shaidar da Global Times ta fitar, HSBC tana sane sarai da mu'malar kamfanin na China da Skycom.
Bankin a cewar rahoton ya zabi ya "hada kai" da gwamantin Amurka don gujewa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, a lokacin da bankin ya amsa laifin shigar da kudaden haram da ya karya takunkumin wanda ya kunshi cuzgunawa Iran.
An umarci Bankin da a lokacin da ya biya tara ta kusan dala biliyan 1.9 ya kuma gujewa duk wata dabi'a irin wannan.
"Hujja ta nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantakar amma da gangan ta sayar da takardun bayanan sirrin abokan mu'amalarta ga bangaren Amurka domin gwamnatin Amurka su iya kawar da kai ga rashin da'ar bankin Birtaniya kuma ba a hukunta shi ba a karkashin Yarjejeniyar da aka Kaddamar ta Laifuka," labarin da jaridar ta bayyana a daya daga cikin rubuce-rubcenta game da batun.
A wani gargadi na harbin iska, jaridar da ke karkashin ikon fadar Beijing ta kara da cewa idan aka tabbatar da laifin mai bayar da rancen na "hada baki" zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a China, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwannin HSBC.
Wannan ba shine karon farko ba da a ka sa bankin a gaba a 'yan makonnin nan.
A watan da ya wuce, an yiwa HSBC kaca-kaca a saboda goyon baya waata sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa na Hong Kong, a garin da kasuwancin ya samo asali kuma yake da fiye da rabin ribarsa.
Bankin ya sha caccaka daga bangarori biyu - daga Yammaci, tare da Mike Pompeo Sakataren Kula da Harkokin Wajen Amurka ya kira tallafawar da zama "kamafanin dan amshin shata," sai kuma Gabas, tare da bangaren China aka rawaito suna cewa tallafinsu "yayi jinkiri"
Masu aikin kashe gobara suna samun nasara akan wutar da ta tashi a gundumar Lassen
Masu aikin kashe gobara na samun nasara kan wasu wutar daji biyu da suka kone sama da eka 30,000 a gundumar Lassen, arewa maso gabashin Sacramento.
Wutar mai ci ganga-ganga, wacce ta taso daga kudancin Adin, an shawo kanta da 40 yayin da ta ci gaba da zama barazana ga gidajne da kiuma gidajen gonaki da kuma hara noma, da dabbobin kiwo da kuma aikin yin katako, jami'an masu aikin kashe gobara na Cal a wata sanarwa ta ranar safiyar Asaba.
Bayan ta kwana hadu ta na ci, gobarar ta kone eka 21,000 kurmus,ta lalata gidaje bakwai tare da aika wasu masu aikin kashe gobara su biyu zuwa asibiti.
A dare daya, masu aikin kashe gobara sun yi amfani da wannan dama na sassaucin yanayi suka gina da kuma inganta layukan tsaro.
Amma ana sa ran iska mai karfi da kuma danshi maras yawa iaya tsawon ranar Asabar.
Yammacin Susanville, wata karamar gobara ta lalata wadansu gine-gine, ta kuma kone kimanin eka 10,000.
Gobarar ta lafa da a cikin daren yayin da masu kashe gobarar suka yi ya aikin karasa karshen burbushinta da kuma inganta hanyoyin dakile ta, a cewar sashen hukumar kula da gandun daji da hana gobara.
Zuwa safiyar ranar Asabar, an ci karfin gobarar da kashi 45 da ta cigaba da  ci har tsawon a kwanaki shida.
A cikin zafin rana, a inda ma'aunin zafin ya kai matakin 90 a Susanville, da akwai mai yiwuwar birbishin tokar wutarta ta sake tayar da wutar.
Yayin da aka kyalle wasu daga cikin mazauna wurin su koma gidajensu, wasu a wuraren kuma za su ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin doka kwashe jama'a na dole daga wurin.
An sallami ma'aikatan kashe gobara su biyu da suka ji ciwo daga asibiti.
Algeria: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - kasara Algeria ta yi rashin dan kishin kasa, kuma jajirtaccen dan gwamarmaya, a cewar Shugaba Tebboune.
Algiers - shugaban jamhuriya, Abdelmajida Tebboune, ya aika da sakon ta'aziyya ga 'yan majalisar dokoki ta gasa na jama'a (APN), Mujaheed Mahmoud Guemam, wanda ya mutu a ranar Juma'a, a cikin ya na mai cewa, Algeria "ta yi rashin dan kishin kasa kuma dan gwagwarmaya wanda ya jajirce kan akidun mutanensa da kuma kasarsa."
A yau Algeria ta yi rashi, rasuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, dan kishin kasa kuma dan gwagwarmaya wanda ya jajirce kan muradai na jama'arsa da kuma kasarsa, mutumin da bai taba ko gezau ba, wanda himmarsa na nan daram daga lokacin da ya daukin makami a kusa da jarumai 'yan uwansa Mujahedeen, har sai Allah ya karbi numfashinsa a wannan rana ta bakin ciki a lokacin da zamu rika mika wuya ga lamarin ubangiji,". Shugaba Tebboune ya rubuta a wasikar da ta'aziyyarsa.
"Marigayi Mahmoud Guemama Allah Ya ji kanshi na daga cikin wasu zababbun wasu mutanen 'yan gwagwarmaya masu karfin imani da suka sadaukar da kansu ga kasarsu" Shugaban Jamhuriyyar yana mai kara fada.
"Marigayin ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa ga kacokam ga samar da 'yancin Algeria daga azabar tsagwaron mulkin mallaka ta hanyar shiga sahun 'yan juyin-juya hali yana cikin ganiyar rayuwarsa a shekarar 1960 a sansanin bayar da hoto na Tahart da ke cikin Wilaya ta VI ma tarihi."
"An san tsohon Shugaban da kuma shaidarsa na tsageranci da kuma jajircewarsa da kuma tsayarwarsa na samar da tunanin hadaddiya kuma yalwatacciyar Algeriya" a cewar Shugaba Tebboune.
A cikin rubutaccen sakon shugaban ya kara da cewa, "A kudancin mai nisa, marigayi Mahmoud Guemama ya yi fice a matsayin mai shiga tsakani, yana shiga tsakani domin ya sasanta tsakanin 'yan uwamu da ke muke kasa daya a duk lokacin da aka kunno wata wutar baraka,"kunno kai.
Shugaban Jamuhuriyyar ya kuma rubuta cew. "Duk wadannan halaye da dabi'u sun samarwa da marigayi Mahoud Guemama karin girmamawa da amincewar mutanen Tamanrasset wadanda suka zabe shi ya wakilcesu a majalisar kasa ta jama'a (APN) akai-akai na tsawon wani lokaci, wanda a lokacin ne ya zama jakada kuma mai kare damuwar da kuma muradan yankin da al'umarta, kai har da wakilci da kuma magana da yawun Algeria da mutanenta".
"Babu wasu kalamai na ta'azziyya da za su iya bayyana alhinin da muke yi na rashin Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, Allah ya yi masa rahama.
Ya bar mu a yau a lokacin da Algeria ta ke da matukar bukatarsa", Shugaban ya fada.
"na rokon Allah mai girma da daukaka da ya lullube marigayin da rahamarsa, ya kuma yi maraba da shi a gidan Aljanna tara da sauran shahidai da kuma bayin Allah nagari.
Ina kuma addu'ar Allah Ya ba iyalinsa da makusantarsa jimirin wannan rashi... dukkanin karfi da iko ya tabbata ga Allah". Shugaban Jamhuriyyar ya kammala.
Zanga-zangar Seattle: Wuta da Feshin Barkono ke tashi a yayin da Dubunnai Sukayo Tattaki Cikin Birnin
SEATTLE - Bayan makonni da aka diba ana gwabzawa tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya na Portland, Ore dandazon mutane kimanin 2,000 sunyi taru a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna kutsawa kan tituna a yayin da suke arangama da yan sanda.
An jikkata jami'an yan sanda uku, an kwantar da daya a asibiti dauke da rauni a kafa sanadiyar abun fashewa, an kuma kame masu tarzoma 16 da la'asar, kamar yadda yan sanda suka bayyana.
Suna dauke da rubuce-rubuce irinsu "Yan tarayya a Koma Gida" sannan suna ihun cewa "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya." masu tarzomar sun tsatstsaya a gurin da za'a dinga daure matasa anan gaba sun kuma ciccinnawa gine-ginen dake gurin wuta.
Wasu kuma sun farfasa windunan shagunan kasuwancin dake kusa.
Yan sanda sunyi fito na fito da dandazon mutanen a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka dinga jefa gurneti mai kashe idanu da feshin barkono kafin su fara diban mutane suna tsarewa.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekaru 52 yar Kirkiland, Wash, tace tun watan Mayu take zanga-zanga akan tituna sai dai kuma tace ta shiga damuwa ganin irin wannan mummunan hanyar da yan sanda suka dauka.
"Ba haka kasar da nayo hjira na dawo take ba," Inji Malama Mukherjee, wacce tazo daga kasar Indiya sama da shekaru 30 da suka shude.
"Sai nake ji a raina kamar kasarmu tana komawa ta kama karya kuma amfani da karfin ikon yan sanda."
Michaud Savage daga Seattle yace ana zanga-zangar ne don nuna kyama ga kananan hukumomi da kuma jami'an tarayya da aka kawo domin kawo karshen tarzomar da taki karewa a Portland.
Mista Savage yace hanyoyin da jami'an tsaro suke amfani da su a Portland, wanda ya hada da yin amfani barkonon tsohuwa da kuma alburushin roba, suna da hatsari kuma bai dace ba.
"Abu ne mai ciwo sosai kuma ya wuce gona da iri," Inji Mista Savage a yayin da yake wanke idanunsa saboda feshin barkono da kuma raunin dake hancinsa da dantsen hannunsa sanadiyar gurneti mai gusar da gani.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun yan sanda dake Minneapolis cikin watan Mayu shi ya haifar da zanga-zangar da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane kan tituna dake birane daban-daban, sai dai zanga-zangar ta ragu a yawancin birane.
Duk da haka zangar-zangar Seattle da Portland ci gaba tayi da karuwa.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle a wani lokaci sun taba bayyana wasu gine-gine da yawa dake unguwar Capitol Hill sun kuma yi ikirarin mayar da yankin mai cin gashin kansa.
Bayan harbe-harbe a gurin yan sanda suka share gurin, zanga-zangar ta lafa.
A halin yanzu ana ci gaba da zanga-zanga a Portland inda tarzomar tafi muni a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya dake cikin birnin.
Bayan Shugaban kasa Trump ya bayar da umarnin zartarwa don a kare mutun-mutumi da kuma dukiyoyin tarayya, sai Hukumar Tsaron cikin Gida ta girke tawagar jami'ai a cikin brnin, wanda suka fara haifar jerin rikice-rikice wanda ya jikkata masu zanga-zangar, babban insifekta janar na bincike yayi kira ga shuwagabbin cikin gida akan jami'an tarayya su janye.
Dandazon masu zanga-zangar sun ninka zuwa dubunnai, sannan kuma ana ci gaba da yin tarzomar a can.
Hukumar tarayya ta girke jami'anta a Seattle cikin wannan makon, inda masu zanga-zangar suka bayyna hakan a matsayin daya daga cikin dalilan yin zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar.
Alhalin zanga-zangar Portland ta tsaya ne a tsakiyar gari, zangar-zangar ranar Asabar ta kewaya cikin yankunan gabashin tsakitar garin, inda kotun tarayya take.
