An yiwa 'yar wasan damben zamani a rukunin UFC Correia rubdugu bayan da ta juyawa abokiyar karawarta baya a bisa kuskure a tunanin cewa zagayen ya kare (hoton bidiyo) - Labaran wasanni na RT
'Wata 'yar Brazil kuma 'yar wasan damben zamani a ajin marasa nauyi tsohuwar mai rike da kambun UFC ta tafka wani kuskure na dan koyo yayin da ta juya baya ga abokiyar karawarta Pannie Kianzad a bisa tunanin cewa zagayen ya kare a karawarsu a tsibirin fight, a karshe ta ragargajeta.
Yayin da karon farko na karawar ta su ya zo karshe a wasan sharar fage a Abu Dhabi, Correia 'yar shekara 37 da haihuwa daga alamu ta kuskure da gargadin dakika goma zuwa karshen zagaye a matsayin karshen zagayen, ta mika hannunta tare da juya bayanta ga Kianzad tana mai tafiya zuwa kusurwarta.
Ba tare da bata lokaci ba 'yar damben ta kasar Sweden ta yi amfani da wannan dama, ta ragargaji abokiyar karawarta da wani naushin hannun dama da sannan ta rufeta da duka hara da hadeta da kejin da aka yi musu.
Fargar cewa ta na cikin hadari, 'yar kasar Brazil din ta farga tare da samun dama da cin galabar wannan barazana ta kuma lallasa Kinzad kafin a kira karshen zagayen na hakika.
Me ya faru a can? in baka yi bani wuri," haka aka ji gungun masu yin sharhi na ESPN+ na ta fada.
Wannan bangare guda daya ne tak na daren takaicin da Correia tsohuwar mai kalubalantar mai rike da kambin ajin marasa nauyi, wacce ta fadi a sakamakon wani hukuncin bai daya da ya kayar da ita wanda kuma shine faduwarta karo na uku a cikin fitarta filin dambe wanda kuma ya bar ta a matsayin 11-5,da kunnen doki daya.
Ga Kianzad 'yar kasar Iran kuwa. 'yar shekara 28, cin nasararta karo na biyu ke nan a jere bayan ta samu nasara kan Jessica-Rose Clark a karawar UFC a wani dare a birnin Moscow a watan Nuwanbar da ta wuce.
