Ooh! A farkon shekarar nan kafofin watsa labarai sun samar tabbaci na daga kudaden shiga a yayin da wannan annoba ta fara tsorata masu talla.
Wasu majiyoyi na cewa kamfanonin suna tattauna hanyoyin samun daidaito wasu manyan koma baya da suka samu, ta hanyar rage kudin hayar da suke biya a wuraren da suke aiki ko kuma ta hanyar cirewa ko rage mafi karancin haraji, wadanda galibi ake gabatarwa kafin a fara sanya hannu a yarjejeniya.
Wata majiyar ta nuna cewa kamfanonin allunan tallace-tallacen za su iya bayar da tabbacin kusan kaso 85 cikin dari na kiyasin kudaden shigarsu na haya.
Wasu kwangilolin suna da sadarar da za ta basu damar su rage mafi karancin tabbaci idan adadin mutanen a wani aiki ya ragu izuwa wani kaso, sai dai ba'a san ko wannan sharadin yana cikin kowacce kwangilar ta yanzu tsakanin kamfanonin talla ba da kuma iyayen gidansu.
A lokaci guda kuma, kamfanonin suna bayar da gwaggwaban ragi ga masu tallace-tallace don su cike guraben da ke kan allunan tallansu da babu komai akai, wanda kuma kwalliya za ta biya kudin sabulu.
Allunan talla a cikin Sydney CBD da kuma wajen garin wandanda galibi ake saka tallace-tallace shida suna ta faman kokarin cike duk wani gurbin da ake da su.
Amma wasu kamfanonin talla - kamar kanfanin oOh! allon talla kamfanin mai mita 40 x 10 a filin jirgin saman Sydney - an inganta shi.
Ooh! Kafofin watsa labarai sun ki su ce komai, sai dai taron Macquarie Austerilia a cikin watan Mayu, ya janyo hankalin ta hanyar nuna cewa sama da dala miliyan 20 a matsayin kayyadajjen kudin hayar da aka samu rage.
