Cutar Korona: An gayawa matafiya daga Spain da su kebe
Daga yanzu matafiya masu zuwa Burtaniya daga Spain dole su kebe na tsawon kwanaki 14, a sabuwar dokar tafiye-tafiye na cutar korona.
An bayyana sune a ranar Asabar bayan karuwar masu kamuwa da kwayar cutar a Spain, inda aka bayar da rahoton sama da mutane 900 suka sake kamuwa a ranar Jumma'a.
Hukumomin kasar Spain sun yi gargadin cewa dawowar cutar a karo na biyu zai iya fin muni kamar yadda manyan birane suke ganin lamarin a yanzu.
Kamfanonin jiragen sama da suka hada da British Airways sun soki matakan a matsakyin wani "abun cikas ga" ga masu shirya hutun shakatawa a Birtaniya.
Ma'aikatar sufuri ta shawarci masu hutun shakatawa a Spain a halin yanzu da su bi dokokin cikin gida, su koma gidajensu lafiya, su kuma bibiyi shafin yanar gizo na tafiye-tafiye na ofishin harkokin waje don meman karin bayani.
Ofishin harkokin wajen yana bada shawara ga duk wata tafiya mai muhimmanci zuwa ga babban garin Spain, haka kuma ka'idojin kebewar sun shafi wadamda suke dawowa daga babban garin Spain, da Tsibiren Canary da kuma Tsibiren Balearic, kamar Majorca da Ibiza.
Ofishin Harkokin waje ya bayar da shawarar sakamakon inshoran tafiye-tafiye.
Daga cikin wanda sabbin dokokin suka shafa har da Sakataren Sufuri Grants Shapps, wanda y afara hutun shakatawarsa a Spain a ranar Asabar.
Ana sa rai zai ci gaba da tafiyar tasa kamar yadda aka tsara sannan sai ya kebe kansa idan ya dawo kamar yadda dokar ta tanadar.
An fara sanya dokar kebe matafiya a Birtaniya ne tun a farkon watan Yuni.
Amma bayan matsin lamba daga bangaren sufurin jirgin sama da kamfanonin sufuri, sai gwamnati ta yanke hukunci inda aka wallafa jerin sunayen kasashen da aka ware daga cikin dokokin.
Kamfanin jirgin saman British Airways yace ya ji "yakaici" a game da sabbin canje-canjen dokoki da shawarwarin, koda yake kamfanin jirgin yace jiragenta su na ci gaba da yin aiki.
Yace matakin ya "jefa shirye-shiryen dubunnan matafiya yan Birtaniya a cikin rudani."
Kungiyar Masu Kula da Filin Jirgin sama sun ce sabbin matakan zasu "kara lalata abinda daman ya riga ya zama lallabe tun bayan sake dawowar fannin sufurin jirgin sama wanda ya ci gaba da fuskantar babban kalubale a tarihinsa."
Babban kamfanin jigila a Birtaniya, Tui, ya fasa tashin jiragensa izuwa babban garin Spain da kuma Tsibiren Canary a ranar Lahadi.
Abokan hulda dake hutu a halin yanzu suna iya dawowa gida a jirgen da suka nufa.
Haka kuma, jirgin kasafin kudi watau EasyJet yace "abun takaici ne" kuma zai dawo cikakken aiyukansa nan da kwanaki masu zuwa.
"Abokan huldar da suka fasa yin tafiya zasu iya sauya jirgi ba tare da wani karin kudi ba ko kuma su karbi adadin kwatankwacin kudin su da suka biya," kamar yadda kamfanin ya fitar a bayanansa.
Wani mai magana da yawun Kungiyar Masu Bulaguron Jiragen Sama watau (Abta) yace sauyin da gwamnati ta yiwa dokar kebewar abun "takaici ne."
"Muna baiwa gwamnati shawara da tayi la'akari ta janye dokokin kebewar nan ga jiragen sama zuwa da dawowa cikin wasu zababbun yankuna wanda suke da karancin kamuwa da cutar, ko kuma gurare kamar su Tsibirin Balearic ko na Canary - wanda suna cikin yankunan mangatutuwan Spain - domin kaucewa yiwa kamfanonin shige da ficen kasar Birtaniya," inji shi.
