Gadar Hadakar ta Sarka ta tsallake kogin Tweed daga Fishwick dake Iyakokin Scotland izuwa Horncliffe dake Northumberland.
Lokacin da aka bude ta a shekarar 1820, ita ce gadar zallar karfe mafi tsawo a duniya mai fadin kafa 449 (mita 137).
Ita ce kuma gadar abun hawa irinta ta farko a Birtaniya.
Sojan Ruwa na sarauniya ne yayi zayyana gadar watau Kaftin Samuel Brown.
Ya samu sahalewa a hukumance sannan ya samar da zallar sarkokin karafa bayan asarar Jirgin Ruwan Sojojin Sarauniya da yayi saboda tsinkewar igiyoyi da ya gamu da ita.
Abokan Gadar Union Chain da kuma Majami'ar Injiniyoyin Zayyana da Gina Hanyoyi da Gada watau (Ice) dake Scotland sun gudanar da bikin shekara dari biyu ana haye ta.
Robert Hunter, daya daga cikin abokan kungiyar, yace: "A gaskiya wannan tana daya daga cikin gadoji mafiya tarihi a duniya kuma ta kasance wani abun ban sha'awa na kere-kere.
" Mun shirya abubuwa da dama domin mu gudanar da bikin, sai dai abun takaici dole ne a fasa yi.
