Akalla ma'aikata 38 ne na wani babban reshen banki na kasa a Tiruchirappali, Tamil Nadu gwajin da a ka yi musu ya nuna suna dauke da cutar Koronabirus, a cewar jami'an bankin da kuma kungiyar al'ummar yakin.
