QB Herbert na cikin 4 daga cikin wadanda Chargers suka zaba suka kuma dauka
COSTA MESA, Calif.  (AP) - Kungiyar Kwallon kafa ta Los Angeles Chargers ta dauki hudu daga cikin sabbin 'yan wasa ciki har da Justin Herbert, sun kuma yarda da shiga wata 'yajejeniya da sauran biyu daga cikin sabbin daukar.
Kungiyar ta Chargers sun samu damar kammala kwatiraginsu da sabbin dauka a ranar Asabar a yayin da suka fara zuwa sansanin horaswa don gudanar atisayen motsa jiki da kuma na kayan aiki.
Tare da Herbert, wanda aka zaba tare da mutane shida cikin wadanda ke kan gaba, kungiyar ta sanar da sa hannu da Joe Reed manyan masu karba da nauyi (zagaye na biyar) da KJ Hill (zagaye na bakwai) tare da dan zagaye na shida Alohi Gilman.
Sun yarda su hade da 'yan sahun farko na tsaron baya Kenneth Murray Jr. da kuma mai dafe baya Joshua Kelley, wanda aka zaba a zagaye na farko.
Herber ya soma da wasanni 42 a Oregon, a inda ya tattare lissafi 29-13 da 10,541 mika kwallo da kuma jimlar taba kasa 108.
Shi ne ya jagoranci kungiyar Ducks zuwa gasar fidda da gwani na Pac-12 a kakar wasan da ya wuce, a ya yi jifa 32, da taba kasa da kuma kama kwallo shida a wasanni 14.
Ya kai koluwar a sana'arsa da kuma nasara kan Wisconsin a Rose Bowl, a inda ya yi guduna tabawa kasa sau uku aka kuma lakabawa wannan kai harin suna MVP.
Herbert zai yi goyayya da tsohon dan wasa Tyrod Taylor da ya soma aiki.
Kungiyar ta Chargers za ta samu sabon dan baya, bayan da Philip Rivers ya tafi ta hukumar kyauta bayan kakan wasanni 14 a matsayin da farko.
Murray wanda ke a matakin na 23 a jimlar wadanda aka dauka bayan Los Angeles ta yi ciniki da New England na su koma zagayen farko.
Ya na cikin rukuni na uku na Associated Press na duk zabin America a kakar wasan da ta wuce bayan jagorantar Sooners da takala 102, ciki har da 69 wanda ya yi shi kadai.
